# Netlify redirects for SPA (Single Page Application)
# This ensures all routes are handled by React Router

# Redirect all requests to index.html for SPA routing
/*    /index.html   200

# Optional: Redirect www to non-www (uncomment if using custom domain)
# https://www.brb-medical-salon.com/*  https://brb-medical-salon.com/:splat  301!

# Optional: Force HTTPS (Netlify does this by default, but can be explicit)
# http://brb-medical-salon.netlify.app/*  https://brb-medical-salon.netlify.app/:splat  301!